Addis Ababa
Covid-19 cases in Africa had reached to 3.26 million as of Monday, the Africa Centres for Disease Control and Prevention (Africa CDC) said.
According to the continental disease control and prevention agency's Africa Covid-19 dashboard, the death toll from the pandemic stood at 78,911 as of Monday, with 2.6 million recoveries.



